<p class="ayah 2-21" id="21" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَـٰٓأَيُّهَا ٱلنَّاسُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">O mankind!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱعْبُدُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">worship</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبَّكُمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your Lord,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the One Who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَلَقَكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">created you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and those [who]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن قَبْلِكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">before you,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَعَلَّكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so that you may</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَتَّقُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">become righteous.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>21<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
