irst rtl" dir="rtl">لِلْكَـٰفِرِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for the disbelievers.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>24<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 2-25" id="25" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَبَشِّرِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And give good news</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to) those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامَنُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believe,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَعَمِلُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and do</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلصَّـٰلِحَـٰتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[the] righteous deeds,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">جَنَّـٰتٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(will be) Gardens,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَجْرِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">flow</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[from]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَحْتِهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">under them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَنْهَـٰرُ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the rivers.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span cl