dir="rtl">رِجْزًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a punishment</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّمَآءِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the sky</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">because</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they were</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَفْسُقُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">defiantly disobeying.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>59<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 2-60" id="60" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">۞ وَإِذِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱسْتَسْقَىٰ مُوسَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Musa asked for water</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِقَوْمِهِۦ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for his people,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَقُلْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[so] We said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱضْرِب</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Strike</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِّعَصَاكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with your staff</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْحَجَرَ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the stone.`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَٱنفَجَرَتْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then gushed forth</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنْهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱثْنَتَا عَشْرَةَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">twelve</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَيْنًا‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">springs.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَدْ عَلِمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Knew</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُلُّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">all</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُنَاسٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) people</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّشْرَبَهُمْ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their drinking place.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُلُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Eat</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱشْرَبُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and drink</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رِّزْقِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) provision (of)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and (do) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَعْثَوْاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">act wickedly</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَرْضِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the earth</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُفْسِدِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir=