<p class="ayah 2-61" id="61" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِذْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلْتُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَـٰمُوسَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`O Musa!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Never (will)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَّصْبِرَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">we endure</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[on]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">طَعَامٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">food</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٲحِدٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) one (kind),</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَٱدْعُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so pray</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for us</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">رَبَّكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to) your Lord</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُخْرِجْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to bring forth</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for us</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">out of what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُنۢبِتُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">grows</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْأَرْضُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the earth,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنۢ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَقْلِهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">its herbs,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَقِثَّآئِهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[and] its cucumbers,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَفُومِهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[and] its garlic,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَعَدَسِهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[and] its lentils,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَبَصَلِهَا‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and its onions.`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَالَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَتَسْتَبْدِلُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Would you exchange</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">that which</sp