<p class="ayah 2-82" id="82" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامَنُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَعَمِلُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and did</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلصَّـٰلِحَـٰتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">righteous deeds,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُوْلَـٰٓئِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَصْحَـٰبُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are the) companions</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْجَنَّةِ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) Paradise;</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِيهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَـٰلِدُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(will) abide forever.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>82<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
