<p class="ayah 2-84" id="84" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِذْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَخَذْنَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">We took</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِيثَـٰقَكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your covenant,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا تَسْفِكُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`You will not shed</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">دِمَآءَكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your blood</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا تُخْرِجُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and (will) not evict</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَنفُسَكُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">yourselves</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">دِيَـٰرِكُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your homes,`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ثُمَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَقْرَرْتُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you ratified</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَنتُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">while you</span></span><span class="word stati