<p class="ayah 2-97" id="97" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Whoever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">is</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَدُوًّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">an enemy</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِّجِبْرِيلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to Jibreel -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَإِنَّهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then indeed he</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَزَّلَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">brought it down</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">on</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَلْبِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">your heart</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِإِذْنِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">by (the) permission</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُصَدِّقًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">confirming</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl"