<p class="ayah 2-110" id="110" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَأَقِيمُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And establish</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلصَّلَوٲةَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the prayer</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَءَاتُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and give</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلزَّكَوٲةَ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[the] zakah.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And whatever</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُقَدِّمُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you send forth</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لِأَنفُسِكُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for yourselves</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">of</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَيْرٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">good (deeds),</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَجِدُوهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you will find it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عِندَ ٱللَّهِ‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">with Allah.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed, Allah</span></span><span class=