<p class="ayah 2-111" id="111" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَقَالُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And they said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Never</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَدْخُلَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will enter</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْجَنَّةَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Paradise</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">except</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">is</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُودًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(a) Jew[s]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَوْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">or</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَصَـٰرَىٰ‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(a) Christian[s].`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تِلْكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">That</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمَانِيُّهُمْ‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) their wishful thinking.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl