<p class="ayah 2-117" id="117" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَدِيعُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(The) Originator</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلسَّمَـٰوَٲتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the heavens</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْأَرْضِ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and the earth!</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَإِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَضَىٰٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He decrees</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمْرًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a matter,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَإِنَّمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[so] only</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَقُولُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He says</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">to it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Be,`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَيَكُونُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and it becomes.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>117<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
