ord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مُسْلِمُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) submissive.`</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>133<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 2-134" id="134" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تِلْكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">This</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُمَّةٌ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(was) a community</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَدْ خَلَتْ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(which) has passed away,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَا كَسَبَتْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what it earned</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَكُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and for you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَسَبْتُمْ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you earned.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تُسْــَٔلُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">you will be asked</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَمَّا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">about what</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَانُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they used to</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَعْمَلُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">do.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>134<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
<p class="ayah 2-135" id="135" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَقَالُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And they said,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كُونُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Be</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُودًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Jews</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَوْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">or</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">نَصَـٰرَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Christians,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَهْتَدُواْ‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(then) you will be guided.`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بَلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`Nay,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِلَّةَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) religion</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِبْرَٲهِــۧمَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) Ibrahim,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَنِيفًا‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(the) upright;</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَمَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top 