<p class="ayah 2-175" id="175" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُوْلَـٰٓئِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Those</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) they who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱشْتَرَوُاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">purchase[d]</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلضَّلَـٰلَةَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[the] astraying</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلْهُدَىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for [the] Guidance,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلْعَذَابَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and [the] punishment</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">بِٱلْمَغْفِرَةِ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for [the] forgiveness.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَمَآ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">So what (is)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَصْبَرَهُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their endurance</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">on</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلنَّارِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the Fire!</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>175<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
