<p class="ayah 2-222" id="222" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيَسْــَٔلُونَكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And they ask you</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَنِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">about</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمَحِيضِ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[the] menstruation.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قُلْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Say,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُوَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">`It</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَذًى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) a hurt,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَٱعْتَزِلُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so keep away (from)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلنِّسَآءَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[the] women</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">during</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْمَحِيضِ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(their) [the] menstruation.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And (do) not</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَقْرَبُوهُنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">approach them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَتَّىٰ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">until</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَطْهُرْنَ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they are cleansed.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَإِذَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Then when</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">تَطَهَّرْنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they are purified,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَأْتُوهُنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">then come to them</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَيْثُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">where</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَمَرَكُمُ ٱللَّهُ‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah has ordered you.`</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِنَّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Indeed,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُحِبُّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">loves</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلتَّوَّٲبِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">those who turn in repentance</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيُ