<p class="ayah 2-245" id="245" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مَّن</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ذَا ٱلَّذِى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is) the one who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُقْرِضُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will lend</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(to) Allah -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">قَرْضًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a loan</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">حَسَنًا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">good,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فَيُضَـٰعِفَهُۥ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">so (that) He multiplies it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَهُۥٓ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">for him -</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَضْعَافًا كَثِيرَةً‌ۚ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">manifolds</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يَقْبِضُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">withholds</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَيَبْصُۜطُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and grants abundance,</span></span><span class="word static