<p class="ayah 2-257" id="257" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱللَّهُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Allah</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَلِىُّ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(is the) Protecting Guardian</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ءَامَنُواْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">believe[d].</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُخْرِجُهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He brings them out</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلظُّلُمَـٰتِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[the] darkness</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">towards</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلنُّورِ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">[the] light.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">وَٱلَّذِينَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">And those who</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">كَفَرُوٓاْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">disbelieve(d)</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَوْلِيَآؤُهُمُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">their guardians</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلطَّـٰغُوتُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are) the evil ones,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">يُخْرِجُونَهُم</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they bring them out</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِّنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلنُّورِ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the light</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">إِلَى</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">towards</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلظُّلُمَـٰتِ‌ۗ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">the darkness.</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أُوْلَـٰٓئِكَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">Those</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">أَصْحَـٰبُ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(are the) companions</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلنَّارِ‌ۖ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">(of) the Fire,</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">هُمْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">they</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">فِيهَا</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">in it</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَـٰلِدُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will abide forever.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span