ْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">and they</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">لَا يُظْلَمُونَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">will not be wronged.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>281<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
